{"tid":415600,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"notebook壞左JJ插沙求問","createTime":"2017-09-27T06:11:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-27T11:46:35.000Z","uid":147105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2a0cb2bbb54134ddd9546155743861eeabcdf13c","tid":415600,"uid":147105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T06:11:21.000Z","msg":"我部華碩成七千蚊買番黎<br />\nhea用左半年<br />\n星期日個日想開機執下文件<br />\n開左唔夠三秒刷一聲跳左掣<br />\n開頭以為冇電<br />\n之後叉叉佢<br />\n發現佢個叉燈唔著<br />\n開機燈仲砍下砍下<br />\n拿左落電腦舖問<br />\n佢今日打黎同我講話係燒底板<br />\n心諗真係有咁化學咁易壞咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想問下大家覺得係咪真係關底板事<br />\n同埋如果壞底板要幾多錢整<br />\n利申有野用完唔記得刪變左待命<br />\n唔知關唔關事"},{"pid":"706358c3cd1664a534a250f03b82a9711e4be399","tid":415600,"uid":147105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T06:13:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba64dfe13373eabc7c3542dd641b063aaba426df","tid":415600,"uid":147105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T06:15:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/f